## Memory System Specs

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Storage needed | ~50MB total |
| Embedding model | 40MB |
| SQLite database | ~5MB base |
| Conversations stored | ~100 before summarization |
| Compression | 50-75% via quantization |

